text: Baltika () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Baltiysky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 719 as of 2010. There are 13 streets. == Geography == It is located 13 km from Iglino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Baltika, Republic of Bashkortostan
